'''美西律'''（{{lang-en|Mexiletine}}）是一種用於治療[[心律不整|異常心律]]、慢性疼痛和某些肌肉僵硬原因的藥物。常見的副作用包括腹痛、胸部不適、睏倦、頭痛和噁心。屬於[[抗心律不整藥|抗心律不整藥物]]的IB類（[[鈉離子通道|鈉離子通道]]阻斷劑）。<ref name="CanaveroBonicalzi2011">{{cite book| first1 = Sergio | last1 = Canavero | first2 = Vincenzo | last2 = Bonicalzi|title=Central Pain Syndrome: Pathophysiology, Diagnosis and Management|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=GMzES57AGnoC&pg=PA286|date=13 October 2011|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-107-01021-5|pages=286–}}</ref>

